name: Humanity
description: After the Earth was completely depleted of its natural resources, massive exploration and colonization campaigns were initiated to find habitable planets where humanity can sow its seeds; creating an entire legion of trained space explorers. You have been selected to become one of the hundreds of brilliant and elite Cadres that would roam the universe looking for potential planets where humans can find the hope to live again. Armed with solar-powered suits and compact spaceships, you are destined to become the source for humanityâ€™s survival. Yet there are dangers that you must fear, for no one knows what the vastness of the universe hides.
